23
00:02:09,929 --> 00:02:12,765
- I can't believe we
didn't take the elevator.

24
00:02:12,765 --> 00:02:15,135
But this is good, this is good.

25
00:02:15,235 --> 00:02:16,736
If you happen to be 20.

26
00:02:16,736 --> 00:02:19,806
- Mom, we're experiencing
Paris, that means walking it.

27
00:02:19,806 --> 00:02:22,342
- This isn't walking,
this is mountain climbing.

28
00:02:22,342 --> 00:02:24,611
- Come on, all the
way to the top.

29
00:02:24,611 --> 00:02:26,146
- [Barbara] This isn't the top?

30
00:02:31,251 --> 00:02:34,554
- [Megan] Summit within
sight, but expedition forced

31
